summary: Just a cme preset of my characters face. Needs Enhanced Character Edit.
descriptionHtml:
Make sure You have Enhanced character edit:
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?]http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?[/url]
and then download this file and extract it. Take the file, which is a _12_commonTriRaces.slot and put it in the CME_saves file.
Dont have that folder? Easy, i had the same problem, start your game in any save and code command [b]showracemenu[/b] and immediately click finish. It will ask for you to save, click any save other than _12_ and save and exit your game. If you dont need that save, delete it after you place this file in there.

Requirements: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35267/?]SG texture renewal[/url]﻿, [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35327/?]Sg female eyebrows[/url], [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/18717/?]Temptress race[/url], [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]the eyes of beauty[/url].
With those, i used [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/53742/?]elsye cme[/url] then tweaked it around.
author: Qualkore
